  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Improved EW-EA to strengthen Disaster Preparedness in Ethiopia</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="2">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">At the end of the project period, web based ICT system will be in place to predict and take early action to unfolding emergencies in target woredas.</narrative>
  </description>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">One of project goals is to establish a decentralized and downscaled climate information flow system. the approach will use to install  and manage four automated weather stations to  facilitate real time data gathering and analysis in  selected woredas  in Gambella and Oromia regions. In addition training will be provided to staffs and target communities in the woredas. NMA will be in charge of managing and monitoring the activities.</narrative>
  </description>
